          'The Atlas is not just about documenting the past—it’s about imagining the future. You will have the opportunity to contribute to a living, evolving resource that helps Toronto rethink its relationship with water and shape a future that is more just, sustainable, and imaginative.',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600132806370-bf17e65e942f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2194&q=80',
      alt: 'Blueprint Image',
    }}
  >
